<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge"/>
    <meta name="msapplication-TileColor" content="#ffffff"/>
    <meta name="msapplication-config" content="favicons/browserconfig.xml"/>
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#ff365c"/>
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="favicons/apple-touch-icon.png"/>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="favicons/favicon-32x32.png"/>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="favicons/favicon-16x16.png"/>
    <link rel="manifest" href="favicons/site.webmanifest"/>
    <link rel="mask-icon" href="favicons/safari-pinned-tab.svg" color="#ff365c"/>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicons/favicon.ico"/>
    <title>AISBERG :: SIGN IN</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:700|Noto+Sans:400,700&amp;amp;subset=cyrillic"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.min.css"/>
  </head>
  <body class="b__sign">
    <div id="preloader"><img src="img/preloader.svg" alt=""/></div>
    <div class="b__sign--aside" data-scrollbar="horizontal">
      <div class="b__sign--info">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col md__8 md__2--offset">
              <h3>Sign Up Now and Get...</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <svg>
                    <use xlink:href="#sign-icon-1"></use>
                  </svg><span>From troubled dreams, he found himself transformed in his bed into a horrible vermin. He lay on his armour-like back, and if he lifted his head a little he could see his brown belly, slightly domed and divided by arches into stiff sections. </span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <svg>
                    <use xlink:href="#sign-icon-2"></use>
                  </svg><span>The bedding was hardly able to cover it and seemed ready to slide off any moment.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <svg>
                    <use xlink:href="#sign-icon-3"></use>
                  </svg><span>From troubled dreams, he found himself transformed in his bed into a horrible vermin. He lay on his armour-like back. </span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="b__sign--content" data-scrollbar="horizontal">
      <div class="flex__column">
        <div class="b__sign--form">
          <div class="form__sign">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col md__8 md__2--offset">
                  <h1> <span>Sign In</span><small>
                      <svg>
                        <use xlink:href="#logo-icon"></use>
                      </svg></small></h1>
                  <p class="text__darkgrey">From troubled dreams, he found himself transformed in phis bed into a horrible vermin.</p>
                  <div class="form__row">
                    <label>Uspername or email</label>
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Enter your username or email here"/>
                  </div>
                  <div class="form__row">
                    <label>Password</label>
                    <input type="password" placeholder="Enter your password here"/>
                  </div>
                  <div class="form__row"><a href="">Forgot password?</a></div>
                  <div class="form__sign--ctrl">
                    <div class="col">
                      <div class="checkbox">
                        <input id="remember" type="checkbox"/>
                        <label for="remember"><span class="icon">
                            <svg>
                              <use xlink:href="#checkbox-icon"></use>
                            </svg></span><span class="label">Remeber me</span></label>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                      <button class="btn cta">Continue</button>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text__center"><span>Don't have an account yet? </span><strong class="text__upper"><a class="cta" href="">SIGN UP now</a></strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="b__sign--footer">
          <p>Aisberg will be listed on major exchanges. See details at <a>CoinMarketCap</a> and <a>Block.cc</a></p>
          <p>Copyright 2018. Aisberg.com <a>Privacy Polycy</a> | <a>Terms & Conditions</a> | <a>F.A.Q.</a> | <a>News</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- SCRIPTS -->
    <script src="js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/main.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/app.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>